org.semanticweb.kaon2.api.logic
Interface Rule

All Superinterfaces:
Axiom, Formula
public interface Rule
extends Formula

Represents a rule in the program. A rule contains an array of head formuale and an array of body formulae. The body formulae are always interpreted conjunctively; however, the head formulae can be interpreted as conjunctively or disjunctively, according to the state of the isHeadConjunctive() flag. For SWRL rules, this flag should be always set to true.
